{"tid":2401674,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"YUI 出道15周年 推出記念唱片：《NATURAL》","createTime":"2021-02-10T02:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T19:42:12.000Z","uid":32934,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"50a21c2d1cade62c0a6c31a55bf7b286adba6782","tid":2401674,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"YUI 出道15周年 推出記念唱片：《NATURAL》2月24日推出 self cover6首名曲<br />\n<br />\n為紀念YUI出道15周年，她將在2月24日推出新迷你專輯《NATURAL》，。唱片中將收錄6首重新編曲的紅典作品，並由YUI的現屬樂隊FLOWER FLOWER製作。(留言區有初回限定版的封面)<br />\n<br />\n《NATURAL》<br />\n收錄曲：<br />\n1.feel my soul<br />\n2.CHE.R.RY<br />\n3.Rolling star<br />\n4.Good-bye days<br />\n5.GLORIA<br />\n6.SUMMER SONG<br />\nBlu-ray收錄：<br />\n「インコのhave a nice dayツアー2020-Streaming Live-」(初回版)<br />\n1.夢<br />\n2.浄化<br />\n3.はなうた<br />\n4.SUMMER SONG<br />\n<br />\n&copy; Sony Music Entertainment (Japan) Inc."},{"pid":"e0a0280d390e9fe652db5d68d742a40a31dab291","tid":2401674,"uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"oh gd bye day 支麻"},{"pid":"792546732d57d8035f3ce6850443700c25ec536c","tid":2401674,"uid":3177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e0a0280d390e9fe652db5d68d742a40a31dab291","tid":2401674,"uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"oh gd bye day 支麻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:30:22.000Z","msg":"哦 goodbyeday 是嗎"},{"pid":"85cdfca0924a9df44af8d9d338032786bd1f6145","tid":2401674,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"回憶...回歸原點 , 時間過得好快 ...15年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0e7c6f8052056f115542ea1baaa2974cd96e17","tid":2401674,"uid":201158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"rolling star<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" clas